{"data":[{"date":"09:27 21/08","title":"Mourinho y\u00eau c\u1ea7u MU b\u00e1n Martial trong 1 tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/mourinho-yeu-cau-mu-ban-martial-trong-1-tuan-toi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u Ed Woodward b\u00e1n sao tr\u1ebb Martial tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda.</h2><h2>Martial ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho y\u00eau c\u1ea7u MU b\u00e1n Martial trong 1 tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mourinho y\u00eau c\u1ea7u MU b\u00e1n Martial trong 1 tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/mourinho-yeu-cau-mu-ban-martial-trong-1-tuan-toi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Anthony Martial g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn h\u01a1n qua t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111\u1ea7u h\u00e8 n\u00e0y sau khi g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu cho Mourinho. Anh r\u1eddi tour du \u0111\u1ea5u M\u1ef9 c\u1ee7a MU t\u1eeb s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u1ee9a con th\u1ee9 hai ra \u0111\u1eddi. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng n\u00f3i l\u00e0 Martial \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n, c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng v\u1ec1 Carrington b\u00e1o danh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMourinho r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu khi Martial kh\u00f4ng tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 tr\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1edbm h\u01a1n. V\u00e0 trong m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/martial-bi-phat-nang-vi-bo-tap-chong-doi-mourinho-172-192498.html\" target=\"_blank\">chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 c\u00f3 \u00fap m\u1edf vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea1t Martial 2 tu\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u01a1ng</span>.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMartial ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a MU \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton khi Alexis Sanchez b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Nh\u01b0ng Martial \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc The Seagulls v\u00e0 b\u1ecb r\u00fat ra kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n sau 1 gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mourinho y\u00eau c\u1ea7u MU b\u00e1n Martial</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Brighton k\u1ebft th\u00fac, t\u1edd Daily Star \u0111\u01b0a tin r\u1eb1ng HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra y\u00eau c\u1ea7u bu\u1ed9c gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Ed Woodward ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n Martial.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 cho r\u1eb1ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Martial kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t y\u00eau c\u1ea7u v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ea7n b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y ti\u1ec1n chi ti\u00eau trong th\u00e1ng M\u1ed9t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u0169ng sau tr\u1eadn thua s\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a MU tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton, HLV Sam Allardyce \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t r\u1eb1ng Martial kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cMartial kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i cho Man United. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 nh\u01b0ng Man United \u0111\u00e3 mua nh\u1ea7m ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1ea5t r\u1ed3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang ta \u0111ang \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y m\u00e0 m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n ch\u1eb3ng kh\u00e1 kh\u1ea9m h\u01a1n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 bao. \u0110\u00e1ng l\u1ebd c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ph\u1ea3i ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n. \u0110\u00e1ng l\u1ebd c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 Leroy Sane. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 vi\u1ec7c c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a Mourinho\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man United:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/victor-lindelof-bat-ngo-tho-lo-uoc-mo-khong-the-tin-duoc-172-194938.html\">Victor Lindelof b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd th\u1ed5 l\u1ed9 \u01b0\u1edbc m\u01a1 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-can-co-trach-nhiem-voi-ke-hoach-mua-sam-cua-minh-172-194925.html\">Mourinho c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m v\u1edbi k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua s\u1eafm c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2605","checkdouble":"194957"},{"date":"09:29 21/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Derby County vs Ipswich 01h45 ng\u00e0y 22/8 (H\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/nhan-dinh-derby-county-vs-ipswich-01h45-ngay-228-hang-nhat-anh-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay Derby County vs Ipswich 01h45 ng\u00e0y 22/8 (V\u00f2ng 4 gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t Anh Championship 2018/19): \u00dd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Derby County vs Ipswich 01h45 ng\u00e0y 228 H\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Derby County vs Ipswich 01h45 ng\u00e0y 228 H\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/Derby-County-vs-Ipswich.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Derby County vs Ipswich</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span>Derby County vs Ipswich: 0-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\nS\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Chelsea, Frank Lampard tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n gi\u00fap Derby County n\u00e2ng cao v\u1ecb th\u1ebf trong m\u1eaft d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn, g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Pride Park Derby County \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n Ipswich c\u00e0ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u. Song, theo gi\u1edbi ph\u00e2n t\u00edch, Derby County kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e1ng tin.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Lampard th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a ch\u01b0a thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c. Sau th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 1-0 \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1, Derby County \u0111\u1ec1u tr\u1eafng tay \u1edf 2 v\u00f2ng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 1-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leeds ngay t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng lo ng\u1ea1i, The Ram ch\u01b0a m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi, nh\u1eadn trung b\u00ecnh 2,33 b\u00e0n thua/tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra, k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2006/07, Derby County kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n bi\u1ebft th\u1eafng Ipswich t\u1ea1i Pride Park, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed 3 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i n\u1ebfm m\u00f9i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. K\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng mai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n- Hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p nhau t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 58 tr\u1eadn, Derby County th\u1eafng 21, h\u00f2a 12, thua 25.<br>\r\n- Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Derby County, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 th\u1eafng 9, h\u00f2a 9, thua 11. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN L\u1ef0C L\u01af\u1ee2NG<br>\r\nDerby County: Chris Martin, Ikechi Anya, Curtis Davies (ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng).<br>\r\nIpswich: Tayo Edun (treo gi\u00f2).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2604","checkdouble":"194959"},{"date":"09:37 21/08","title":"HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/hlv-park-hang-seo-tiec-nuoi-vi-chan-thuong-cua-do-hung-dung.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u00e0i Ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i Vi\u1ec7t Nam VOV s\u1eafp tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb n\u1eafm b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng ASIAD 2018 t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 r\u1ebb.</h2><h2>VOV s\u1eafp c\u00f3 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD 2018<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb Zing, T\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c VOV, \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ebf K\u1ef7 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD 2018. VOV v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n xong v\u1edbi KJSM World Corp v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn ch\u1ed1t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb n\u1eafm b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng ASIAD 2018 t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb n\u1eafm b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng ASIAD 2018 t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/lo-dien-don-vi-nam-ban-quyen-phat-song-asiad-2018-tai-viet-nam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>VOV s\u1eafp tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh\u00a0\u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb n\u1eafm b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng ASIAD 2018 t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ngu\u1ed3n tin kh\u00e1c cho bi\u1ebft m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 VOV chi ra \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD 2018 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 1.7 tri\u1ec7u USD (x\u1ea5p x\u1ec9 39.5 t\u1ec9 VN\u0110). M\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 r\u1ebb so v\u1edbi con s\u1ed1 4 tri\u1ec7u USD m\u00e0 VTV cho bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0a ra khi\u1ebfn hai b\u00ean kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua ASIAD 2018 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu th\u00f4ng tin VOV \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c theo d\u00f5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain tr\u00ean s\u00f3ng truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh h\u1ee3p ph\u00e1p. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, c\u00e1c m\u00f4n th\u1ec3 thao kh\u00e1c c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Vi\u1ec7t Nam tranh t\u00e0i c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfu r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>K\u1ebft th\u00fac nh\u1eefng tranh c\u00e3i<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e0i n\u00e0o \u1edf Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng ASIAD 2018 khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i theo d\u00f5i di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u qua c\u00e1c k\u00eanh chi\u1ebfu \"l\u1eadu\". \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam thu h\u00fat nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi quan t\u00e2m h\u01a1n c\u1ea3.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 xem b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \"chui\" l\u00e0m d\u1ea5y l\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u tranh c\u00e3i. Ph\u00eda VTV \u0111\u01b0a ra ph\u1ea3n h\u1ed3i r\u1eb1ng v\u00ec \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c ra gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n ch\u1ea5t l\u00e0 \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng mua b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 cho r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i xem \"chui\" l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng x\u1ea5u h\u1ed5.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, vi\u1ec7c xem qua c\u00e1c k\u00eanh kh\u00f4ng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t, b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn ho\u1eb7c ti\u1ebfng n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i ho\u1eb7c ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn NHM m\u1ea5t h\u1ee9ng ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o. N\u1ebfu VOV c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfu ASIAD 2018 r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i tr\u00ean s\u00f3ng truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh s\u1ebd gi\u00fap ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t nh\u1eefng tranh c\u00e3i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-thanh-cong-cung-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-194961.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tiec-nuoi-vi-chan-thuong-cua-do-hung-dung-168-194960.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-nu-thai-lan-vao-tu-ket-asiad-du-trang-tay-o-bang-viet-nam-168-194956.html\">\u0110T n\u1eef Th\u00e1i Lan v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Asiad d\u00f9 tr\u1eafng tay \u1edf b\u1ea3ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-bahrain-noi-dieu-bat-ngo-ve-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-194953.html\">HLV Bahrain n\u00f3i \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-asiad-2018-ngay-hom-nay-218-cua-doan-ttvn-472-194942.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u ASIAD 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 21/8 c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n TTVN</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bac-si-cua-olympic-viet-nam-ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-xuan-truong-ngoi-du-bi-168-194910.html\">B\u00e1c s\u0129 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2603","checkdouble":"194960"},{"date":"10:15 21/08","title":"HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/vff5479-15341729950901227889727.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c gi\u00fap c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ef1 tin l\u00e0 l\u00fd do Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi 3 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Pakistan, Nepal v\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. \u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD trong nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m qua. Ngo\u00e0i y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t cao c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00e0 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 th\u0103ng hoa.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/vff5479-15341729950901227889727.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Park Hang Seo</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, HLV Park Hang Seo chia s\u1ebb: \u201cC\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft g\u00ec \u0111\u00e2u. T\u00f4i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng m\u1edf l\u00f2ng v\u00e0 th\u1eadt th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. T\u00f4i nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i b\u1edfi s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i th\u00ec s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec. D\u00f9 th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf c\u0169ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f4i l\u00fac t\u00f4i h\u01a1i lo l\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ko \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ea5y \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f4i nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh v\u1edbi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 v\u1ec1 tinh th\u1ea7n Vi\u1ec7t Nam, s\u1ef1 nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft, quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m v\u00e0 \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft. \u0110\u00e3 l\u00e0 th\u1eed th\u00e1ch c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i hay th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua nhi\u1ec1u th\u0103ng tr\u1ea7m n\u00ean t\u00f4i c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ec3 chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. \u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eeb b\u1ecf m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u0169ng cho bi\u1ebft \u00f4ng t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. HLV Park Hang Seo c\u0169ng k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1eadp trung, nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau xa h\u01a1n \u1edf ASIAD 18.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng sau khi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y b\u1ecb g\u00e3y ng\u00f3n ch\u00e2n c\u00e1i. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u00f4ng Park c\u0169ng tin t\u01b0\u1edfng 19 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1 thay ph\u1ea7n H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng tr\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h30 ng\u00e0y 23 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 g\u1eb7p Bahrain. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao v\u1ec1 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c l\u1eabn kinh nghi\u1ec7m, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tiec-nuoi-vi-chan-thuong-cua-do-hung-dung-168-194960.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/hlv-park-hang-seo-tiec-nuoi-vi-chan-thuong-cua-do-hung-dung.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tiec-nuoi-vi-chan-thuong-cua-do-hung-dung-168-194960.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng</span><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf r\u00f5 s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng trong...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-nu-thai-lan-vao-tu-ket-asiad-du-trang-tay-o-bang-viet-nam-168-194956.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/dt-nu-thai-lan-vao-tu-ket-asiad-du-trang-tay-o-bang-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-nu-thai-lan-vao-tu-ket-asiad-du-trang-tay-o-bang-viet-nam-168-194956.html\">\u0110T n\u1eef Th\u00e1i Lan v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Asiad d\u00f9 tr\u1eafng tay \u1edf b\u1ea3ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0 trong m\u01a1 m\u1edbi x\u1ea3y ra \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt v\u1edbi \u0110T n\u1eef Th\u00e1i Lan khi h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f3 v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ed9i h\u1ea1ng 3 c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-bahrain-noi-dieu-bat-ngo-ve-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-194953.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/hlv-bahrain-noi-dieu-bat-ngo-ve-dt-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-bahrain-noi-dieu-bat-ngo-ve-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-194953.html\">HLV Bahrain n\u00f3i \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng quan tr\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Malaysia, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Olympic Bahrain \u00f4ng Samir Chammam cho bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh ch\u01b0a t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u g\u00ec v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2602","checkdouble":"194961"},{"date":"10:07 21/08","title":"HLV Klopp n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \"tr\u1ea3m\" Fabinho","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/hlv-klopp-noi-gi-sau-khi-tiep-tuc-tram-fabinho.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Klopp x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng t\u00e2n binh Fabinho b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Liverpool \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Palace v\u00ec l\u00fd do chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 chi ra h\u01a1n 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Fabinho t\u1eeb Monaco h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V Liverpool k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Selhurst Park \u0111\u00eam qua. Nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Fabinho l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong danh s\u00e1ch 18 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Crystal Palace.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tr\u1ea3m Fabinho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tr\u1ea3m Fabinho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/hlv-klopp-noi-gi-sau-khi-tiep-tuc-tram-fabinho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Fabinho b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1ea3i th\u00edch v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra, Klopp chia s\u1ebb: <strong>\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a vi\u1ec7c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y qua tu\u1ea7n kh\u00e1c. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec v\u1edbi Fabinho. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng\u201d.</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf Liverpool trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a West Ham, Fabinho \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng anh hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Anfield.<br>\r\n<em><br>\r\n\u201cKhi t\u00f4i t\u1edbi Liverpool, t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u1edf h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ed1t cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cN\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t. Trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n giao h\u1eefu, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c nhau. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cV\u1eady n\u00ean nh\u00ecn chung t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Crystal Palace, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p West Ham. C\u00f3 v\u1ebb c\u1ed7 m\u00e1y c\u1ee7a Klopp \u0111ang ch\u1ea1y t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i n\u00e0o, \u00edt nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Liverpool:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-crystal-palace-02-liverpool-172-194948.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn Crystal Palace 0-2 Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/lien-tuc-toa-sang-mo-salah-van-bi-thay-che-172-194946.html\">Li\u00ean t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng, Mo Salah v\u1eabn b\u1ecb th\u1ea7y ch\u00ea</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2601","checkdouble":"194962"},{"date":"10:29 21/08","title":"N\u00f3ng: Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u00ean s\u00f3ng truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/19/lo-dien-don-vi-nam-ban-quyen-phat-song-asiad-2018-tai-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u00e0i Ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i Vi\u1ec7t Nam VOV s\u1eafp tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb n\u1eafm b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng ASIAD 2018 t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 r\u1ebb.</h2><h2>VOV s\u1eafp c\u00f3 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD 2018<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb Zing, T\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c VOV, \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ebf K\u1ef7 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD 2018. VOV v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n xong v\u1edbi KJSM World Corp v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn ch\u1ed1t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb n\u1eafm b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng ASIAD 2018 t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb n\u1eafm b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng ASIAD 2018 t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/lo-dien-don-vi-nam-ban-quyen-phat-song-asiad-2018-tai-viet-nam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>VOV s\u1eafp tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh\u00a0\u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb n\u1eafm b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng ASIAD 2018 t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ngu\u1ed3n tin kh\u00e1c cho bi\u1ebft m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 VOV chi ra \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ASIAD 2018 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 1.7 tri\u1ec7u USD (x\u1ea5p x\u1ec9 39.5 t\u1ec9 VN\u0110). M\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c coi l\u00e0 r\u1ebb so v\u1edbi con s\u1ed1 4 tri\u1ec7u USD m\u00e0 VTV cho bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0a ra khi\u1ebfn hai b\u00ean kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua ASIAD 2018 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu th\u00f4ng tin VOV \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c theo d\u00f5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Bahrain tr\u00ean s\u00f3ng truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh h\u1ee3p ph\u00e1p. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, c\u00e1c m\u00f4n th\u1ec3 thao kh\u00e1c c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Vi\u1ec7t Nam tranh t\u00e0i c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfu r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>K\u1ebft th\u00fac nh\u1eefng tranh c\u00e3i<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e0i n\u00e0o \u1edf Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng ASIAD 2018 khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i theo d\u00f5i di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u qua c\u00e1c k\u00eanh chi\u1ebfu \"l\u1eadu\". \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam thu h\u00fat nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi quan t\u00e2m h\u01a1n c\u1ea3.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 xem b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \"chui\" l\u00e0m d\u1ea5y l\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u tranh c\u00e3i. Ph\u00eda VTV \u0111\u01b0a ra ph\u1ea3n h\u1ed3i r\u1eb1ng v\u00ec \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c ra gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n ch\u1ea5t l\u00e0 \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng mua b\u1ea3n quy\u1ec1n. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 cho r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i xem \"chui\" l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng x\u1ea5u h\u1ed5.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, vi\u1ec7c xem qua c\u00e1c k\u00eanh kh\u00f4ng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t, b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn ho\u1eb7c ti\u1ebfng n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i ho\u1eb7c ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn NHM m\u1ea5t h\u1ee9ng ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o. N\u1ebfu VOV c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfu ASIAD 2018 r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i tr\u00ean s\u00f3ng truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh s\u1ebd gi\u00fap ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t nh\u1eefng tranh c\u00e3i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-thanh-cong-cung-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-194961.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tiec-nuoi-vi-chan-thuong-cua-do-hung-dung-168-194960.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-nu-thai-lan-vao-tu-ket-asiad-du-trang-tay-o-bang-viet-nam-168-194956.html\">\u0110T n\u1eef Th\u00e1i Lan v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Asiad d\u00f9 tr\u1eafng tay \u1edf b\u1ea3ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-bahrain-noi-dieu-bat-ngo-ve-dt-olympic-viet-nam-168-194953.html\">HLV Bahrain n\u00f3i \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-asiad-2018-ngay-hom-nay-218-cua-doan-ttvn-472-194942.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u ASIAD 2018 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 21/8 c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n TTVN</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bac-si-cua-olympic-viet-nam-ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-xuan-truong-ngoi-du-bi-168-194910.html\">B\u00e1c s\u0129 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2600","checkdouble":"194963"},{"date":"10:24 21/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Swansea vs Leeds 01h45 ng\u00e0y 22/8 (H\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t Anh 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/nhan-dinh-swansea-vs-leeds-01h45-ngay-228-hang-nhat-anh-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay Swansea vs Leeds 01h45 ng\u00e0y 22/8 (V\u00f2ng 4 gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t Anh Championship 2018/19): \u00dd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Swansea vs Leeds 01h45 ng\u00e0y 228 H\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t Anh 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Swansea vs Leeds 01h45 ng\u00e0y 228 H\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t Anh 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/Swansea-vs-Leeds.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Swansea vs Leeds</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span>Swansea vs Leeds: 2-0<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Swansea l\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i H\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t Anh m\u00f9a n\u00e0y sau khi r\u1edbt xu\u1ed1ng t\u1eeb Premier league. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Wales h\u1ea1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m s\u1edbm tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a t\u1edbi. Qua 3 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Swansea \u0111\u1ea1t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n: 2 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, 1 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a v\u00e0 t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi x\u1ebfp \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 7 tr\u00ean BXH.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00f2ng n\u00e0y, Swansea s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Leeds, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean cho t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 th\u0103ng h\u1ea1ng Premier League. Th\u1ebf l\u1ef1c m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 m\u01a1 v\u1edbi 3 tr\u1eadn to\u00e0n th\u1eafng, ghi 9 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi 2 l\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn, Leeds United \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ea1ch 6 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 4 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng theo ch\u00e2u \u00c1. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, do r\u1edbt xu\u1ed1ng t\u1eeb Premier League n\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Wales c\u00f3 th\u1eeba b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m, b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 l\u0103n l\u1ed9n t\u1ea1i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo ch\u00e2u \u00c1, 10 tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, Swansea th\u1eafng 6. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Leeds m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u00fang 3 l\u1ea7n trong 10 tr\u1eadn s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Liberty v\u1eabn s\u00e1ng c\u1eeda h\u01a1n \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, Swansea th\u1eafng 2 tr\u1eadn, thua 2 v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 2 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec1u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN<br>\r\nSwansea: Nordfeldt, Roberts, Hoorn, Fernandez, Olsson, Celina, Fulton, Carroll, Asoro, McBurnie, McKay.<br>\r\nLeeds United: Farrell, Douglas, Berardi, Ayling, Phillips, Klich, Hernandez, Saiz, Alioski, Roofe.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2599","checkdouble":"194964"},{"date":"10:37 21/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Rotherham vs Hull 01h45 ng\u00e0y 22/8 (H\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/nhan-dinh-rotherham-vs-hull-01h45-ngay-228-hang-nhat-anh-201819.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay Rotherham vs Hull 01h45 ng\u00e0y 22/8 (V\u00f2ng 4 gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t Anh Championship 2018/19): \u00dd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Rotherham vs Hull 01h45 ng\u00e0y 228 H\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Rotherham vs Hull 01h45 ng\u00e0y 228 H\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Anh 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/Rotherham_vs_Hull_City.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Rotherham vs Hull</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span>Rotherham vs Hull: 2-0<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Rotherham l\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00ean h\u1ea1ng t\u1ea1i Championship 2018/19 t\u1eeb League One. Do \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau cao nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.\u00a0 Sau 3 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Rotherham gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 thua 2 (\u0111\u1ec1u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch), th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ea1m ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, Rotherham United \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao khi to\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ea3 7 l\u1ea7n ti\u1ebfp kh\u00e1ch g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Hull City l\u1ea1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ec7 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng c\u1ea3 6 chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHull City l\u1ea1i c\u00f2n kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i m\u00f9a n\u00e0y khi ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 3 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e3 qua. H\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 1-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Sheffield Wednesday v\u00e0 thua Aston Villa, Blackburn. \u201cNh\u1eefng ch\u00fa h\u1ed5\u201d l\u00fac n\u00e0y s\u1edf h\u1eefu v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 22/24 tr\u00ean BXH.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Hull City \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Rotherham 15 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 quan khi h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4, h\u00f2a 3 v\u00e0 thua 8. V\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ec7 nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, vi\u1ec7c Hull City c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Rotherham kh\u00f4ng kh\u1ea3 thi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<br>\r\nRotherham: Rodak, Vyner, Wood, Raggett, Mattock, Ajayi, Taylor, Vaulks, Palmer, Williams.<br>\r\nHull City: McGregor, Clark, Mac Donald, Dawson, Aina, Irvine, Larsson, Diomande, Evandro, Bowen, Dicko.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2598","checkdouble":"194965"},{"date":"11:01 21/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh QPR vs Bristol City 01h45 ng\u00e0y 22/8 (H\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t Anh 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/nhan-dinh-qpr-vs-bristol-city-01h45-ngay-228-hang-nhat-anh-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay QPR vs Bristol City 01h45 ng\u00e0y 22/8 (V\u00f2ng 4 gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t Anh Championship 2018/19): \u00dd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh QPR vs Bristol City 01h45 ng\u00e0y 228 H\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t Anh 2019 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh 