u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd g\u1ed3m ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb ho\u1eb7c thi\u1ebfu kinh nghi\u1ec7m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Bristol City, h\u1ecd t\u00edch c\u1ef1c h\u01a1n QPR ch\u00fat \u00edt.\u00a0 Sau 3 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Lee Johnson m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m, hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 19 tr\u00ean BXH. Tuy nhi\u00ean Bristol l\u1ea1i ch\u01a1i s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch c\u1ef1c t\u1ec7 (kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng 13 tr\u1eadn xa nh\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t Anh). <br>\r\n<br>\r\nSong ngo\u00e0i m\u00e0n kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ec7, QPR c\u00f2n \u0111ang g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 l\u1edbn khi vi ph\u1ea1m lu\u1eadt c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n ph\u1ea1t l\u00ean t\u1edbi 42 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Loftus Road c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n v\u1edbi nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb g\u1ea1t kh\u1ecfi gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh. Trong t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Steven McClaren \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2597","checkdouble":"194966"},{"date":"11:13 21/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh BATE Borisov vs PSV Eindhoven 02h00 ng\u00e0y 22/8 (Champions League 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/21/nhan-dinh-bate-borisov-vs-psv-eindhoven-02h00-ngay-228-champions-league-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>BATE Borisov vs PSV Eindhoven l\u00fac 02h00 ng\u00e0y 22/8 (V\u00f2ng playoff c\u00fap C1/Champions League 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh BATE Borisov vs PSV Eindhoven 02h00 ng\u00e0y 228 c\u00fap C1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh BATE Borisov vs PSV Eindhoven 02h00 ng\u00e0y 228 c\u00fap C1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/BATE-Borisov-vs-PSV-Eindhoven.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">BATE Borisov vs PSV Eindhoven</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>BATE Borisov vs PSV Eindhoven: 1-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\nL\u00e0 Nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 H\u00e0 Lan n\u00ean PSV Eindhoven \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0o th\u1eb3ng v\u00f2ng play-off Champions League. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, BATE Borisov ph\u1ea3i b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u tham d\u1ef1 Champions League t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 2. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, PSV Eindhoven \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 2 m\u00f9a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c Champions League. B\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t BATE Borisov tham d\u1ef1 v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 3 m\u00f9a (m\u00f9a 2015-16). V\u00ec v\u1eady, kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u khi PSV Eindhoven \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a PSV Eindhoven c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Mark van Bommel \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG H\u00e0 Lan 2018/19 v\u1edbi 2 tr\u1eadn to\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Nh\u01b0ng Champions League lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00e1c. 8 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e0y, Nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 H\u00e0 Lan kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng (h\u00f2a 4, thua 4). <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, h\u00e0nh trang m\u00e0 BATE Borisov mang \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u1ea1ch 12 tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng (th\u1eafng 8, h\u00f2a 4). \u1ede Champions League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Belarus c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng thua 4 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc HJK Helsinki v\u00e0 Qarabag (th\u1eafng 2, h\u00f2a 2).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00ednh ri\u00eang \u1edf Champions League, BATE Borisov \u0111ang duy tr\u00ec m\u1ea1ch 7 tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, h\u1ecd c\u00f2n th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Belarus n\u00ean ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i bung s\u1ee9c cho tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u00eam nay. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00e0n so t\u00e0i n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng b\u1edfi BATE Borisov v\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t. 4/5 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Belarus ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 t\u1ed1i \u0111a 2 b\u00e0n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN<br>\r\n+ BATE Borisov (4-3-3): Shcherbitski - Rios, Filipenko, Filipovic, Volodjko - Yablonski, Baga, Dragun - Ivanic, Stasevich, Signevich.<br>\r\n+ PSV Eindhoven (4-2-3-1): Zoet - Dumfries, Schwaab, Viergever, Angelino - Hendrix, Rosario - Lozano, Pereiro, Bergwijn - De Jong.<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2596","checkdouble":"194967"},{"date":"07:02 21/08","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay (21/8/2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-218