t/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n Premier League, Mohamed Salah \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng gi\u00fap Liverpool v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua West Ham 4-0. L\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u01b0\u1edbc Crystal Palace \u1edf v\u00f2ng 2, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ai C\u1eadp c\u00f2n t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng h\u01a1n th\u1ebf. Anh tham gia tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o c\u1ea3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00e0 The Kop c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Salah ki\u1ebfm v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty \u0111\u1ec3 James Milner th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ph\u00fat 45. T\u1edbi ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd th\u1ee9 3, l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 11 c\u1ee7a Liverpool c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 Sadio Mane \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Salah d\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 nghi\u00eam kh\u1eafc h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Salah d\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 nghi\u00eam kh\u1eafc h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/Salah-bi-Klopp-che.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Salah v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 nghi\u00eam kh\u1eafc</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra, c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh Salah l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t t\u1ea5m th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf cho Liverpool. T\u1eeb m\u1ed9t pha b\u1ee9t \u0111i nhanh nh\u1eb9n, anh bu\u1ed9c Aaron Wan-Bissaka ph\u1ea3i ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi m\u00ecnh s\u00e1t v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m v\u00e0 b\u1ecb tru\u1ea5t quy\u1ec1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Klopp ch\u01b0a h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Liverpool, Salah v\u1eabn b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn. \u0110i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh l\u00e0 c\u00fa l\u1ed1p b\u00f3ng v\u1ecdt x\u00e0 sau \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n d\u00e0i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Naby Keita. V\u00e0 HLV Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Salah v\u1eabn b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 ch\u01b0a h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e0n v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, nh\u01b0ng Mo Salah c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng&rdquo;, Klopp n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean. &ldquo;D\u00f9 sao, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p trong c\u1ea3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;X\u00e9t tr\u00ean kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh t\u1eadp th\u1ec3, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Salah ph\u1ea3i tham gia nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam th\u1ee9 7 t\u1edbi, Liverpool s\u1ebd c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Brighton t\u1edbi s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 \u1edf v\u00f2ng 3 Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Crystal Palace 0-2 Liverpool (V\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19):<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_279653\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/8/21/liverpool-crystal-palace-100554359_1200_96.mp4&amp;autoplay=false&amp;urlParent=http://bongdanet.vn/video/crystal-palace-0-2-liverpool-premier-league-ngoai-hang-anh-vong-2-tbd71154\" data-type=\"video-iframe\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2594","checkdouble":"194946"},{"date":"07:36 21/08","title":"Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn Crystal Palace 0-2 Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/de-bruyne-len-tieng-ve-chan-thuong-mat-nua-mua-giai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-w