v\u00e0 h\u00f2a 3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Palace \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 16 sau 20 l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng thu\u1ed9c nh\u00f3m &ldquo;Big Six&rdquo; t\u1edbi s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 (h\u00f2a 2).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Roy Hodgson ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 100 t\u1ea1i Premier League v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng (th\u1eafng 87, h\u00f2a 65).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Wan-Bissaka \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Palace nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf t\u1ea1i Premier League (20 tu\u1ed5i, 267 ng\u00e0y).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- James Milner \u0111\u00e3 n\u1edbi r\u1ed9ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh (48 tr\u1eadn, th\u1eafng 38 v\u00e0 h\u00f2a 10).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- Milner \u0111\u00e3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf 13 trong s\u1ed1 15 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Premier League, 9 cho Liverpool.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n- C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ghi 8 b\u00e0n li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i Premier League \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m 11m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Crystal Palace 0-2 Liverpool (V\u00f2ng 2 Premier League 2018/19):<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table class=\"embedMedia\" id=\"embedMedia_279653\" style=\"width:100%;\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%;\" align=\"center\"><iframe src=\"https://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=bongda24h&amp;vid=premierleague/2018/8/21/liverpool-crystal-palace-100554359_1200_96.mp4&amp;autoplay=false&amp;urlParent=http://bongdanet.vn/video/crystal-palace-0-2-liverpool-premier-league-ngoai-hang-anh-vong-2-tbd71154\" data-type=\"video-iframe\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" oallowfullscreen=\"\" msallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"400\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2593","checkdouble":"194948"},{"date":"07:57 21/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 21/8: Barca \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00e0y \u0111\u00f3n Pogba","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-218-barca-dinh-ngay-don-pogba.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 21/8.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Real t\u00ednh \"\u0111\u00e1nh \u00fap\" sao tr\u1ebb Dortmund.</strong> Real Madrid \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 \u0111\u1ec3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Julian Weigl c\u1ee7a Borussia Dortmund. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 'Sergio Busquets m\u1edbi', Weigl s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Los Blancos m\u1ea5t \u0111i s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 75 tri\u1ec7u Euro.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Barca t\u00ednh \u0111\u00f3n Pogba v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1. </strong>T\u1edd Don Balon \u0111\u01b0a tin, Barcelona s\u1ebd ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i Paul Pogba t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m sau thay v\u00ec ngay h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. M\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Pogba v\u1edbi HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c M.U ch\u01b0a b\u00e1n anh ngay \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 v\u00ec h\u1ecd ch\u01b0a t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 218 Barca \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00e0y \u0111\u00f3n Pogba h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 218 Barca \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00e0y \u0111\u00f3n Pogba h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-188-pogba-duoc-thuong-lon-neu-tu-choi-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Pogba c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1edbi Barca v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 t\u1edbi</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>\"Harry Maguire \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf MU\". </strong>Jonny Evans ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Harry Maguire, \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i Leicester City. C\u1ef1u ng\u00f4i sao Man United kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1 cho nh\u1eefng \u00f4ng l\u1edbn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c2u bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 m\u00ecnh t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nV\u00ec Karius su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Alisson. </strong>Jurgen Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng mua th\u00eam th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi v\u00e0 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Loris Karius. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, c\u1ef1u HLV Dortmund \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Arsenal nh\u1eafm trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga.</strong> Theo Daily Mirror, Arsenal mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga Igor Diveev c\u1ee7a Ufa. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 19 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u khi kho\u00e1c \u00e1o U20 Nga v\u00e0 Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1eed tuy\u1ec3n tr\u1ea1ch vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn x\u1ee9 b\u1ea1ch d\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 theo d\u00f5i anh thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Firmino cung khong chiu kem canh voi thanh tich tuong tu Salah\" title=\"Firmino c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu k\u00e9m c\u1ea1nh v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 Salah\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/25/roberto-firmino-day-la-mua-giai-tot-nhat-trong-su-nghiep-cua-toi.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Firmino mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Liverpool l\u00e2u d\u00e0i</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Firmino mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Liverpool l\u00e2u d\u00e0i.</strong> Trong kho\u1ea3ng 1 n\u0103m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n th\u00f4ng tin Roberto Firmino \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barcelona \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft. Tuy nhi\u00ean, trong m\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y cho bi\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai l\u00e2u d\u00e0i c\u1ee7a anh n\u1eb1m \u1edf Liverpool khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Dortmund nh\u1eafm \"h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\" Barca. </strong>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Barcelona, Paco Alcacer \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Borussia Dortmund xem l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb gi\u1edd t\u1edbi h\u1ebft k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng t\u1ea1i Barca.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2592","checkdouble":"194949"},{"date":"08:43 21/08","title":"HLV Bahrain n\u00f3i \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/21/hlv-bahrain-noi-dieu-bat-ngo-ve-dt-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng quan tr\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Malaysia, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Olympic Bahrain \u00f4ng Samir Chammam cho bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh ch\u01b0a t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u g\u00ec v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</h2><h2>HLV Bahrain kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1\u00a0\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Bahrain ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-2 qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Malaysia \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1i 20/8.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, HLV \u0111\u1ed9i Bahrain \u00f4ng Samir Chammam \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, song v\u1ecb n\u00e0y c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra lo \u00e2u khi ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft nhi\u1ec1u th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Bahrain kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Bahrain kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/21/089549700_1524748953-20180426_150959.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Olympic Bahrain th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y chia s\u1ebb: \u201cN\u00f3i chung t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Bahrain \u0111\u1ebfn ASIAD 2018 v\u1edbi t\u1ea7m nh\u00ecn cho t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. Trong tay t\u00f4i l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t tr\u1ebb.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110a ph\u1ea7n h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i sinh n\u0103m 1997, 1998. C\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb h\u01a1n sinh n\u0103m 1999 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi sinh n\u0103m 2000. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 Olympic Tokyo 2020 v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n ch\u00fa t\u00e2m v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00f3\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 8 n\u0103m, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Bahrain t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ASIAD. Khi \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng do HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-1, sau c\u00e1c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 Thanh Trung. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Bahrain c\u0169ng gi\u00fap Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 ASIAD. \u0110i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 c\u00e1c th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 \u2018\u0111\u00e0n anh\u2019 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Bahrain s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra 19 gi\u1edd 30 ng\u00e0y 23/8 t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Patriot Patriot Candrabhaga, th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Bekasi, t\u1ec9nh T\u00e2y Java. M\u1eddi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u00f3n xem.<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bac-si-cua-olympic-viet-nam-ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-xuan-truong-ngoi-du-bi-168-194910.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/bac-si-cua-olympic-viet-nam-ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-xuan-truong-ngoi-du-bi.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bac-si-cua-olympic-viet-nam-ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-xuan-truong-ngoi-du-bi-168-194910.html\">B\u00e1c s\u0129 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb</span><br />\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng trong n\u01b0\u1edbc, b\u00e1c s\u1ef9 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam Tr\u1ea7n Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh vi\u1ec7c Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/toi-do-cua-nhat-ban-an-tuong-voi-toc-do-cua-cau-thu-olympic-viet-nam-168-194906.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/toi-do-cua-nhat-ban-an-tuong-voi-toc-do-cua-cau-thu-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/toi-do-cua-nhat-ban-an-tuong-voi-toc-do-cua-cau-thu-olympic-viet-nam-168-194906.html\">T\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br />\r\nTrao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, Yuta Kamiya - ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n thua c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Hoa anh \u0111\u00e0o \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tro-ly-than-can-cua-hlv-park-hang-seo-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-ha-nhat-ban-168-194894.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/tro-ly-than-can-cua-hlv-park-hang-seo-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-ha-nhat-ban.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/tro-ly-than-can-cua-hlv-park-hang-seo-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-ha-nhat-ban-168-194894.html\">Tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd th\u00e2n c\u1eadn c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft h\u1ea1 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span><br />\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd th\u00e2n c\u1eadn c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo \u1edf \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2591","checkdouble":"194953"}]}